<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">


<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Pathfinder</title>

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/styles.css" type="text/css">
</head>

<body>
    <header class="header">
      <h1 class="title">Pathfinder</h1>
    </header>

	<div class="currHead">
		<div class="header-item">
			<h2>Instructions</h2>

				1. &nbspTo add walls, click on any square in the grid.<br>
				2. &nbspTo set the start and end points, click on the corresponding buttons and then click on the desired squares in the grid.<br>
				3. &nbspTo clear the grid, click on the "clear" button.<br>
				4. &nbspTo select the algorithm to be used, click on the drop down menu and select the desired algorithm.<br>
				5. &nbspTo begin the algorithm, click on the "start algorithm" button.<br>
				
		
		</div>
		<div class="header-item">
			<h2>Algorithms</h2>
			<p>Current searching algorithms include: </p>
			<br>
			
				Dijkstra's algorithm
				<br>
				Breadth-first search
				<br>
				Depth-first search
				<br>
				
		</div>

	</div>
    <main class="main">
      <div class="settings">
		<button id="colorBtn">Wall</button>
        <button id="eraserBtn">Erase</button>
        <button id="clearBtn">Clear</button>
        <div id="sizeValue" class="size-value">16 x 16</div>
        <input id="sizeSlider" type="range" value="16" min="1" max="64" />
      </div>
      <div id="grid" class="grid"></div>
	  <div class="settings">
		<button id="startBtn">Start</button>
        <button id="endBtn">End</button>
        <button id="startAlgoBtn">Start algorithm</button>
		<select name="algos" id="algos">
			<option value="dijkstra">Dijkstra</option>
			<option value="temp">temp</option>
			<option value="bfs">bfs</option>
			<option value="dfs">dfs</option>
		  </select>
      </div>
    </main>
    <script src="/public/script.js"></script>
  </body>
